ne" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1088_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1089_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1091_">You can easily create a customer account by clicking on the “Log-in” found in the navigation bar. By this, you’ll be able to save your cart and sign-in to view your order whenever you want.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1092_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1093_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="cb42416a-69f4-449b-99a9-d42c3469e8dd" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>How do I retrieve my password?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="cb42416a-69f4-449b-99a9-d42c3469e8dd" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1095_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1096_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1098_">Please use the "Forgot my password" option located on the login page on our website. It will walk you through resetting passwords.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-expandable="true" style="display:none" data-pf-type="TabsContent" class="sc-gjNHFA hBngIv pf-1099_"><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1100_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1101_"><h4 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-1102_ header"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1104_">The Emma Original Mattress</span></h4><h6 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-1105_ header"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1107_">About the Emma Original Mattress</span></h6><div class="sc-iCfMLu dkvyUF pf-1108_ pf-icon-left" data-scrolling="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion"><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1109_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1110_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="c8e1a6b7-cf21-4124-9c80-db4645d27423" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>What makes the Emma Original Mattress special?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="c8e1a6b7-cf21-4124-9c80-db4645d27423" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1112_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1113_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1115_">The Emma Original, with over 75 product awards, is composed of three layers. Its AIRGOCELL® foam technology dissipates sweat and absorbs heat so that you sleep cool and comfortable. Its HALO® Memory Foam has 3 zones that adapt to your body shape and has motion isolation technology so that you get better pressure relief and uninterrupted sleep. Its HRX® Supreme Foam has 5 adaptive cutouts that distribute your body weight evenly so that you get full body support.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1116_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1117_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="249c80db-4645-4274-a307-e36e75e67b4a" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>How is the Emma Original Mattress constructed?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="249c80db-4645-4274-a307-e36e75e67b4a" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1119_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1120_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1122_">The Emma Original Mattress consists of 5 different layers:</span></p><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1123_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1124_"><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:1px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-fXEqDS fVXmAe pf-1125_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1126_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1128_">The Plush Emma UltraDry® Original Cover with its temperature-regulating technology allows for a breathable cover and makes mattress maintenance easy.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1129_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1131_">The AIRGOCELL® foam has an open-pore cell structure and enables pleasant air circulation while keeping you cool, even on warm nights</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1132_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1134_">Motion-isolating HALO® Memory foam uses 3-zone support to balance out pressure points that will help you get a better night's sleep.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1135_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1137_">The Emma HRX Supreme® Foam is engineered to last for years and serves as the foundational support of the mattress.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1138_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1140_">Emma Edge Support provides a reinforced perimeter that not only helps prevent restless and active sleepers from falling off at night but also helps all sleepers easily sit up in the morning.</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1141_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1142_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="443c633f-9419-4df9-a9a8-6deac9b4a258" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>What certifications does the Emma Original Mattress have?
</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="443c633f-9419-4df9-a9a8-6deac9b4a258" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1144_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1145_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1147_">The foam used to make the Emma Original mattress is CertiPUR-US® and Class I (16.0.93305) of STANDARD 100 by OEKO-TEX®.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1148_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1149_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="f969a86d-eac9-44a2-98ca-6ff86befef7a" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>What are the sizes available for the Emma Original Mattress?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="f969a86d-eac9-44a2-98ca-6ff86befef7a" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1151_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1152_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1154_">Our Emma Original Mattress comes in 6 sizes– find one that suits you!</span></p><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1155_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1156_"><ul style="--text-indent:0px;--line-spacing:1px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-fXEqDS fVXmAe pf-1157_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1158_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1160_">Twin: 38” x 75” x 10’’ (35 lbs) - Best for children, teens, or anyone under six feet tall.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1161_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1163_">Twin XL: 38” x 80” x 10’’ (37 lbs) - Best for growing children and/or teens.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1164_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1166_">Full: 54” x 75” x 10’’ (48 lbs) - Best for individuals or couples looking for something compact yet&nbsp;</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1167_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1169_">Queen: 60” x 80” x 10’’ (58 lbs) - Best for individuals or couples who want extra space.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1170_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1172_">King: 76” x 80” x 10’’ (72 lbs) - Best for families who sleep together.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1173_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1175_">California King: 72” x 84” x 10’’ (72 lbs) - Best for maximized space and comfort for your family and even pets.</span></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1176_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1177_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1178_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1180_">If you’re still undecided on what size to get, we’d be more than willing to help you out. You may reach out to our Customer Care agents from 6 AM - 9 PM EST through our available channels:
</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1181_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1182_"><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:1px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-fXEqDS fVXmAe pf-1183_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1184_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1186_">Email: support@emma-sleep.ca&nbsp;</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1187_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1189_">Landline: +1-888-585-3662</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1190_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1192_">or speak directly with an agent using our live-chat feature on our website.</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1193_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1194_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="8f75e696-cce5-445c-a54c-dfea51b94f8d" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Does the Emma Original Mattress fit on any bed frame?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="8f75e696-cce5-445c-a54c-dfea51b94f8d" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1196_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1197_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1199_">Yes, the Emma Original Mattress will fit in the majority of the appropriate bed frames.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1200_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1201_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="5c654cdf-ea51-494f-8d54-f46ec1bd2e80" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Is the Emma Original Mattress fire retardant?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="5c654cdf-ea51-494f-8d54-f46ec1bd2e80" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1203_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1204_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1206_">Yes, the Emma Original mattress is compliant with the Canadian fire safety regulations and does not use chemicals to meet this requirement.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1207_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1208_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="4f8d54f4-6ec1-4d2e-80fc-427402c6274d" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Does it need a topper or bed cover?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="4f8d54f4-6ec1-4d2e-80fc-427402c6274d" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1210_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1211_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1213_">You do not need a topper or a bed cover to use the Emma Original Mattress. However, if you would like to control the softness/firmness of your mattress, our Firm-to-Soft Reversible Topper will help you achieve just that. For more information, you may view our Topper <a href="/products/emma-topper" target="_blank">here.
</a></span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1214_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1215_"><h6 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-1216_ header"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1218_">Is the Emma Original Mattress right for you?</span></h6><div class="sc-iCfMLu dkvyUF pf-1219_ pf-icon-left" data-scrolling="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion"><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1220_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1221_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="c6274d2c-a929-4631-9b80-b57e1b4a41c4" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Does the foam smell?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="c6274d2c-a929-4631-9b80-b57e1b4a41c4" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1223_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1224_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1226_">Like all new products, the Emma Original mattress has a slight "new" smell at the start which will wear out over time. However, rest assured, the foams in our Emma Original have passed both CertiPUR-US® &amp; OEKO-TEX® certifications, which mean that those smells are temporary and harmless as we are free of harmful chemicals such as formaldehyde, phthalates, and flame retardants, as verified by an independent third-party organization.
<br><br>&nbsp;However, if the odor is bothering you, allow your mattress to air out for 24 hours, at which point the odor should subside. Should you have any more concerns, please reach out to our Customer Care agents from 6 AM - 9 PM EST through our available channels:
</span></p><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1227_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1228_"><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:1px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-fXEqDS fVXmAe pf-1229_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1230_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1232_">Email: support@emma-sleep.ca&nbsp;</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1233_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1235_">Landline: +1-888-585-3662</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1236_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1238_">or speak directly with an agent using our live-chat feature on our website.</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1239_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1240_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="21a728db-2edd-4446-862b-fec0fb27390b" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>How firm is the Emma Original Mattress?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="21a728db-2edd-4446-862b-fec0fb27390b" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1242_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1243_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1245_">The Emma Original Mattress is considered ‘Medium Firm’. To help you out, imagine sleeping in cloudy comfort where we’re soft enough to feel comfortable and cozy while having that firmness to support your body as if someone was cuddling you to sleep.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1246_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1247_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="46862bfe-c0fb-4739-8ba1-b91b5c199eff" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Is the Emma Original Mattress vegan?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="46862bfe-c0fb-4739-8ba1-b91b5c199eff" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1249_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1250_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1252_">The foam used to make the Emma Original mattress is CertiPUR-US® and Class I (16.0.93305) of STANDARD 100 by OEKO-TEX®.Yes, the Emma Original Mattress is 100 % vegan and does not contain any animal-based materials. Unfortunately, the mattress is inedible.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1253_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1254_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="390ba1b9-1b5c-499e-bf0f-1f99ba75b061" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>I have back or neck pain, is Emma Original Mattress the right mattress for me?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="390ba1b9-1b5c-499e-bf0f-1f99ba75b061" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1256_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1257_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1259_">We understand that needs vary by individuals so we offer 365 days to test the Emma Original mattress risk-free. That way you can decide if it is best for your situation.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1260_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1261_"><h6 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-1262_ header"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1264_">How do I take care of my Emma Original Mattress?</span></h6><div class="sc-iCfMLu dkvyUF pf-1265_ pf-icon-left" data-scrolling="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion"><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1266_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1267_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="75b06199-a53c-4230-874f-58a20173b5e6" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Can I wash my Emma Original Mattress?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="75b06199-a53c-4230-874f-58a20173b5e6" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1269_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1270_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1272_">Yes, but you may only wash the Plush Emma UltraDry® Original Cover of your mattress. Just open the zip and separate the top from the bottom part. For specific information, you may see their individual wash-label details.</span></p><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1273_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1274_"><div data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-jObWnj dWwBay pf-1275_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0562/9873/3706/t/22/assets/wash-labels-1658749111058_1200x.png?v=1658749112" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0562/9873/3706/t/22/assets/wash-labels-1658749111058.png?v=1658749112 1536w" width="637" height="189" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, 320px" loading="lazy"/></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1276_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1277_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="58a20173-b5e6-4c2f-825f-02cfe4ea91da" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Is the mattress considered a medical device?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="58a20173-b5e6-4c2f-825f-02cfe4ea91da" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1279_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1280_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1282_">No, the Emma Original mattress is not a medical device.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1283_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1284_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="2f025f02-cfe4-4a91-9a21-06e5366be010" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>How long can my Emma mattress stay in the box for?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="2f025f02-cfe4-4a91-9a21-06e5366be010" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1286_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1287_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1289_">The Emma Original mattress shouldn't be left rolled up in the box for more than four weeks after delivery as this may damage your mattress.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1290_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1291_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="91da2106-e536-4be0-907e-9f0e70e139b8" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Do I need to flip and ventilate it?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="91da2106-e536-4be0-907e-9f0e70e139b8" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1293_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1294_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1296_">No. Flipping your Emma Original mattress is not necessary and the white top-cover and AIRGOCELL® layer should always remain on top. The three layers of foam serve as an especially long-lived function of support, so the usual flipping of the mattress isn’t necessary. The special breathability and open-cell character of the core materials provide a self-contained ventilation system, keeping the mattress aerated.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1297_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1298_"><h6 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-1299_ header"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1301_">Returns &amp; Delivery</span></h6><div class="sc-iCfMLu dkvyUF pf-1302_ pf-icon-left" data-scrolling="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion"><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1303_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1304_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="e139b8f0-7fd0-4839-a87d-fc314c0511d6" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>How do I return my Emma Original Mattress?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="e139b8f0-7fd0-4839-a87d-fc314c0511d6" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1306_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1307_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1309_">You may return your Emma Original Mattress within 365 nights of receiving your product. When you want to return your Emma Original Mattress, please contact our Customer Care agents from 6 AM - 9 PM EST through our available channels:
</span></p><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1310_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1311_"><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:1px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-fXEqDS fVXmAe pf-1312_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1313_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1315_">Email: support@emma-sleep.ca&nbsp;</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1316_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1318_">Landline: +1-888-585-3662</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1319_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1321_">or speak directly with an agent using our live-chat feature on our website.</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1322_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1323_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="61338786-79d4-4a7d-80d4-4787ea33e036" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Does the Emma Original Mattress have a warranty?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="61338786-79d4-4a7d-80d4-4787ea33e036" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1325_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1326_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1328_">The Emma Original Mattress has a 10-year-warranty upon receipt. For more information on warranty claims, please visit our <a href="/pages/terms-and-conditions" target="_blank">Terms and Conditions</a> or contact our Customer Care agents from 6 AM - 9 PM EST through our available channels:
</span></p><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1329_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1330_"><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:1px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-fXEqDS fVXmAe pf-1331_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1332_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1334_">Email: support@emma-sleep.ca&nbsp;</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1335_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1337_">Landline: +1-888-585-3662</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1338_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1340_">or speak directly with an agent using our live-chat feature on our website.</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-expandable="true" style="display:none" data-pf-type="TabsContent" class="sc-gjNHFA hBngIv pf-1341_"><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1342_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1343_"><h4 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-1344_ header"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1346_">The Emma Original Mattress</span></h4><h6 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-1347_ header"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1349_">About the Emma Climax® Hybrid</span></h6><div class="sc-iCfMLu dkvyUF pf-1350_ pf-icon-left" data-scrolling="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion"><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1351_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1352_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="f1d7e707-c144-499c-a0aa-57cc5797aaa3" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>What Makes the Emma Climax® Hybrid special?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="f1d7e707-c144-499c-a0aa-57cc5797aaa3" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1354_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1355_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1357_">The Emma Climax® Hybrid is composed of six layers designed for heavy sleepers and couples alike. It showcases our new Climax® Pocketed Springs, which are individually wrapped coils engineered for the optimum tension and bounce to provide strong enough support for all types of sleepers and activities in bed. Aside from the pocketed springs, it has the award-winning AIRGOCELL® foam technology that dissipates sweat and absorbs heat so that nights are only hot (and steamy) when you want them to.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1358_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1359_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="9ca0aa57-cc57-47aa-a3cf-8ac874eb50af" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>How is the Emma Climax® Hybrid constructed?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="9ca0aa57-cc57-47aa-a3cf-8ac874eb50af" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1361_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1362_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1364_">The Emma Climax Hybrid®  consists of 6 different layers:
</span></p><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1365_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1366_"><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:1px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-fXEqDS fVXmAe pf-1367_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1368_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1370_">The UltraDry® Pillowtop Cover has climate-regulating and moisture-wicking technology that allows for a breathable cover and makes mattress maintenance easy.
</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1371_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1373_">The AIRGOCELL® Hypersoft Comfort Layer has an open-pore cell structure and enables air circulation and dissipates body heat so nights only get hot (and steamy) when you want them to.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1374_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1376_">The Climax® Transition Layer is an adaptive memory foam with over 100 supportive points and 5 zoned cutouts that adapts to your body to provide optimal spinal alignment and pressure relief</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1377_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1379_">The Climax® Pocketed Springs are individually wrapped pocketed coils designed for the optimum tension and bounce to provide strong enough support for all types of sleepers. It also enhances airflow for better breathability and a cool night’s sleep.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1380_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1382_">The HRX Supreme® Edge Support provides a reinforced perimeter that not only helps prevent restless and active sleepers from falling off at night but also helps all sleepers easily sit up in the morning.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1383_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1385_">The HRX Supreme® Support Layer is a base foam layer that is guaranteed to provide support and withstand decades of use by heavy sleepers and couples alike.</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1386_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1387_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="45ed2fb7-156e-412e-abaf-18a9991b36d8" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>What certifications does the Emma Climax® Hybrid have?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="45ed2fb7-156e-412e-abaf-18a9991b36d8" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1389_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1390_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1392_">The foam used to make the Emma Original mattress is CertiPUR-US® certified.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1393_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1394_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="2eabaf18-a999-4b36-98e6-e44685e28be2" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>What are the sizes available?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="2eabaf18-a999-4b36-98e6-e44685e28be2" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1396_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1397_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1399_">Our Emma Climax® Hybrid comes in 6 sizes– find one that suits you!&nbsp;</span></p><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1400_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1401_"><ul style="--text-indent:0px;--line-spacing:1px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-fXEqDS fVXmAe pf-1402_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1403_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1405_">Twin: 38” x 75” x 10’’ (35 lbs) - Best for children, teens, or anyone under six feet tall.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1406_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1408_">Twin XL: 38” x 80” x 10’’ (37 lbs) - Best for growing children and/or teens.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1409_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1411_">Full: 54” x 75” x 10’’ (48 lbs) - Best for individuals or couples looking for something compact yet&nbsp;</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1412_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1414_">Queen: 60” x 80” x 10’’ (58 lbs) - Best for individuals or couples who want extra space.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1415_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1417_">King: 76” x 80” x 10’’ (72 lbs) - Best for families who sleep together.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1418_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1420_">California King: 72” x 84” x 10’’ (72 lbs) - Best for maximized space and comfort for your family and even pets.</span></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1421_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1422_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1423_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1425_">If you’re still undecided on what size to get, we’d be more than willing to help you out. You may reach out to our Customer Care agents from 6 AM - 9 PM EST through our available channels:
</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1426_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1427_"><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:1px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-fXEqDS fVXmAe pf-1428_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1429_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1431_">Email: support@emma-sleep.ca&nbsp;</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1432_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1434_">Landline: +1-888-585-3662</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1435_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1437_">or speak directly with an agent using our live-chat feature on our website.</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1438_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1439_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="d93dc7f2-3443-4a88-862a-d0781dced0cb" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Does the Emma Climax® Hybrid fit on any bed frame?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="d93dc7f2-3443-4a88-862a-d0781dced0cb" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1441_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1442_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1444_">Yes, the Emma Climax® Hybrid will fit in the majority of the appropriate bed frames.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1445_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1446_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="88862ad0-781d-4ed0-8b6b-3bb6772e2b40" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Is the Emma Climax® Hybrid fire retardant?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="88862ad0-781d-4ed0-8b6b-3bb6772e2b40" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1448_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1449_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1451_">Yes! The Emma Climax® Hybrid is constructed to comply with applicable safety laws and is fire retardant. We make sure to keep your safety in mind when engineering our products.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1452_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1453_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="d0cb6b3b-b677-4e2b-8014-79d717d8537e" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Does the Emma Climax® Hybrid need a topper or bed cover?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="d0cb6b3b-b677-4e2b-8014-79d717d8537e" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1455_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1456_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1458_">You do not need a topper or a bed cover for the Emma Climax® Hybrid. The use of a topper might affect the bounciness of the mattress. However, if you would like to control the softness/firmness of your mattress, our Firm-to-Soft Reversible Topper will help you achieve just that. For more information, you may view our Topper&nbsp;<a href="/products/emma-topper" target="_blank">here.
</a></span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1459_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1460_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="04e031ee-0d84-46c8-8de9-ac46624125d9" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>What’s the difference between the Emma Original Mattress and the Emma Climax® Hybrid?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="04e031ee-0d84-46c8-8de9-ac46624125d9" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1462_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1463_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1465_">The award-winning Emma Original Mattress is recommended for all sleepers, regardless of your sleeping position. Made with the breathable AIRGOCELL® and HRX Supreme base layer, the Emma Original distributes body weight evenly, relieves pressure and eliminates motion transfer for your best night’s sleep.
<br><br>The Emma Climax® Hybrid is recommended for sleepers who want extra support, and for those who want to do more than sleep. It combines the award-winning comfort, zero motion transfer, zoned support and pressure relief of our Emma Original with the breathability, bounce and extra support of our  Climax® Pocketed Springs. 

Both Emma mattresses are considered medium-firm, offering the perfect mix of comfort and support.
</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1466_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1467_"><h6 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-1468_ header"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1470_">Is the Emma Climax® Hybrid right for you?</span></h6><div class="sc-iCfMLu dkvyUF pf-1471_ pf-icon-left" data-scrolling="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion"><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1472_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1473_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="d8537e4b-ecc6-4afa-b33c-7846bd1b152a" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Does the foam smell?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="d8537e4b-ecc6-4afa-b33c-7846bd1b152a" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1475_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1476_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1478_">Like all new products, the Emma Climax® Hybrid has a slight "new" smell at the start which will wear out over time. However, rest assured, the foams in our mattress have passed both CertiPUR-US® &amp; OEKO-TEX® certification. This means that those smells are temporary and harmless, as the foams are free of harmful chemicals such as formaldehyde, phthalates, and flame retardants, as verified by an independent third-party organization.
<br><br>&nbsp;However, if the odor is bothering you, allow your mattress to air out for 24 hours, at which point the odor should subside. Should you have any more concerns, please reach out to our Customer Care agents from 6 AM - 9 PM EST through our available channels:
</span></p><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1479_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1480_"><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:1px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-fXEqDS fVXmAe pf-1481_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1482_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1484_">Email: support@emma-sleep.ca&nbsp;</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1485_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1487_">Landline: +1-888-585-3662</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1488_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1490_">or speak directly with an agent using our live-chat feature on our website.</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1491_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1492_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="5b958434-fbf2-4a46-a16d-698dc62de478" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>How firm is the Emma Climax® Hybrid?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="5b958434-fbf2-4a46-a16d-698dc62de478" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1494_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1495_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1497_">The Emma Climax® Hybrid is considered to be ‘Medium Firm’, a 6 on a 1-10 scale, 1 being the softest. To help you out, imagine sleeping in cloudy comfort where we’re soft enough to feel comfortable and cozy while having that firmness to support your body as if someone was cuddling you to sleep.
</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1498_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1499_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="46616d69-8dc6-4de4-b83c-510e43e205e2" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Is the Emma Climax® Hybrid vegan?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="46616d69-8dc6-4de4-b83c-510e43e205e2" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1501_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1502_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1504_">Yes, the Emma Original Mattress is 100 % vegan and does not contain any animal-based materials.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1505_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1506_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="e4783c51-0e43-4205-a2b2-5effadcbace2" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>I have back or neck pain, is the Emma Climax® Hybrid the right mattress for me?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="e4783c51-0e43-4205-a2b2-5effadcbace2" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1508_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1509_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1511_">The Climax® Hybrid is constructed with the Climax® Transition Layer with over 100 supportive points and 5 zoned cutouts that contours and adapts to your body for optimal spinal alignment and pressure relief.  We understand that needs vary by individuals so we offer 365 days to test the Emma Climax® Hybrid risk-free. That way you can decide if it is best for your situation.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1512_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1513_"><h6 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-1514_ header"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1516_">How do I take care of my Emma Climax® Hybrid?</span></h6><div class="sc-iCfMLu dkvyUF pf-1517_ pf-icon-left" data-scrolling="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion"><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1518_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1519_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="cbace2f5-6e4a-4664-89c2-9c8bbecbf287" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Can I wash my Emma Climax® Hybrid?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="cbace2f5-6e4a-4664-89c2-9c8bbecbf287" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1521_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1522_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1524_">Yes, but you may only wash the Plush Emma UltraDry® Original Cover of your mattress. Just open the zip and separate the top from the bottom part. For specific information, you may see their individual wash-label details.</span></p><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1525_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1526_"><div data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-jObWnj dWwBay pf-1527_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0562/9873/3706/t/22/assets/wash-labels-1658749111058_1200x.png?v=1658749112" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0562/9873/3706/t/22/assets/wash-labels-1658749111058.png?v=1658749112 1536w" width="637" height="189" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, 320px" loading="lazy"/></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1528_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1529_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="9c8bbecb-f287-4dd5-b1d9-43fade6aac0c" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Is the mattress considered a medical device?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="9c8bbecb-f287-4dd5-b1d9-43fade6aac0c" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1531_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1532_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1534_">No, the Emma Climax® Hybrid is not a medical device.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1535_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1536_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="d5b1d943-fade-4aac-8c22-bf1767b3f640" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>How long can my Emma Climax® Hybrid stay in the box for?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="d5b1d943-fade-4aac-8c22-bf1767b3f640" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1538_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1539_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1541_">The Emma Climax® Hybrid shouldn't be left rolled up in the box for more than four weeks after delivery as this may damage your mattress.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1542_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1543_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="ac0c22bf-1767-43f6-8071-17e5912da89a" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Do I need to flip and ventilate it?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="ac0c22bf-1767-43f6-8071-17e5912da89a" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1545_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1546_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1548_">No need for the extra hassle! Flipping your Emma Climax® Hybrid is not necessary and the Ultradry® Pillowtop Cover should always remain on top. The mattress is specially engineered with a specific top to bottom layering to give you zero motion transfer, pressure relief and zoned support for years of comfortable night’s sleep.&nbsp;</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1549_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1550_"><h6 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-1551_ header"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1553_">Returns &amp; Delivery</span></h6><div class="sc-iCfMLu dkvyUF pf-1554_ pf-icon-left" data-scrolling="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion"><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1555_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1556_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="2da89afa-b8e7-4f99-b0e9-136c1e21b1e9" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>How do I return my Emma Climax® Hybrid?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="2da89afa-b8e7-4f99-b0e9-136c1e21b1e9" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1558_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1559_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1561_">You may return your Emma Climax® Hybrid within 365 nights of receiving your product. When you want to return your Emma Climax® Hybrid, please contact our Customer Care agents from 6 AM - 9 PM EST through our available channels:
</span></p><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1562_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1563_"><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:1px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-fXEqDS fVXmAe pf-1564_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1565_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1567_">Email: support@emma-sleep.ca&nbsp;</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1568_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1570_">Landline: +1-888-585-3662</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1571_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1573_">or speak directly with an agent using our live-chat feature on our website.</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1574_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1575_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="28996231-4e4c-4931-8414-5af68fbbafa8" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Does the Emma Climax® Hybrid have a warranty?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="28996231-4e4c-4931-8414-5af68fbbafa8" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1577_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1578_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1580_">The Emma Climax® Hybrid has a 10-year-warranty upon receipt. For more information on warranty claims, please visit our <a href="/pages/terms-and-conditions" target="_blank">Terms and Conditions</a> or contact our Customer Care agents from 6 AM - 9 PM EST through our available channels:
</span></p><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1581_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1582_"><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:1px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-fXEqDS fVXmAe pf-1583_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1584_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1586_">Email: support@emma-sleep.ca&nbsp;</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1587_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1589_">Landline: +1-888-585-3662</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1590_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1592_">or speak directly with an agent using our live-chat feature on our website.</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-expandable="true" style="display:none" data-pf-type="TabsContent" class="sc-gjNHFA hBngIv pf-1593_"><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1594_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1595_"><h4 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-1596_ header"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1598_">Upholstered Bed Frame&nbsp;</span></h4><h6 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-1599_ header"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1601_">About the Upholstered Bed Frame&nbsp;</span></h6><div class="sc-iCfMLu dkvyUF pf-1602_ pf-icon-left" data-scrolling="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion"><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1603_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1604_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="95a0bebb-12b2-448b-a299-6efe914fedaa" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Is the Upholstered Bed Frame non-flammable?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="95a0bebb-12b2-448b-a299-6efe914fedaa" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1606_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1607_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1609_">Yes, it is non-flammable. It has also passed the cigarette test, which means that it does not easily catch on fire.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1610_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1611_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="8be2996e-fe91-4fed-aa11-a49366423c0e" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Is the Upholstered Bed Frame vegan?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="8be2996e-fe91-4fed-aa11-a49366423c0e" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1613_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1614_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1616_">Yes, the Upholstered Bed Frame is 100 % vegan and does not contain any animal-based materials, nor is tested on animals. </span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1617_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1618_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="edaa11a4-9366-423c-8ef7-677146d0f2ba" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Can I buy it without the headboard? </span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="edaa11a4-9366-423c-8ef7-677146d0f2ba" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1620_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1621_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1623_">Unfortunately, not at the moment. If you decide not to use it, you can always store it. The Upholstered Bed Frame even offers you enough storage space to place it underneath the bed, if you decide not to use it. </span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1624_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1625_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="3c0ef767-7146-40f2-bab0-eb2429c54f65" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Can I use an electric slatted frame? </span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="3c0ef767-7146-40f2-bab0-eb2429c54f65" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1627_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1628_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1630_">No. The slats that are delivered with the bed cannot be replaced by an electric slatted frame due to the construction of the bed.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1631_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1632_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="f2bab0eb-2429-454f-a5bd-6cce952f72d2" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Do you offer different colors?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="f2bab0eb-2429-454f-a5bd-6cce952f72d2" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1634_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1635_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1637_">At present, we offer only the color grey for the Upholstered Bed Frame.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1638_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1639_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="4f65bd6c-ce95-4f72-927c-0862df12e47b" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>How durable is the Upholstered Bed Frame?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="4f65bd6c-ce95-4f72-927c-0862df12e47b" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1641_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1642_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1644_">The Upholstered Bed Frame is highly durable and has gone through several durability tests during its development to ensure its quality. It has been tested to be able to withstand up to 500 lbs of force - meaning it can hold up a lot of weight. </span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1645_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1646_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="72d27c08-62df-42e4-bbf9-a12944d27e53" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Can I place the Upholstered Bed Frame in the middle of the room?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="72d27c08-62df-42e4-bbf9-a12944d27e53" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1648_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1649_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1651_">Yes, but we recommend placing the Emma Upholstered Bed Frame against a wall. This will offer you the maximum amount of stability for your bed frame. </span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1652_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1653_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="e47bf9a1-2944-427e-9385-18fb609ef23c" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>How long is the guarantee? </span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="e47bf9a1-2944-427e-9385-18fb609ef23c" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1655_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1656_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1658_">We have a 60 night-trial and 5 years warranty on the product (excluding the screws). </span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1659_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1660_"><h6 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-1661_ header"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1663_">Is the Emma Upholstered Bed Frame right for you?&nbsp;</span></h6><div class="sc-iCfMLu dkvyUF pf-1664_ pf-icon-left" data-scrolling="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion"><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1665_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1666_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="9ef23c00-59f7-415c-98a5-386bc6790ac6" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Can the bed be used without a headboard? Can I use my own?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="9ef23c00-59f7-415c-98a5-386bc6790ac6" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1668_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1669_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1671_">Yes, the Upholstered Bed Frame may be used without a headboard and you may also use your own headboard. After both boxes have arrived, you can decide whether to use the headboard or not. The Upholstered Bed Frame even offers you enough storage to put it underneath the bed, if you decide not to use it.&nbsp;</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1672_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1673_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="5c58a538-6bc6-490a-86ea-446c4565c9ca" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Can I use my own slats for the bed frame?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="5c58a538-6bc6-490a-86ea-446c4565c9ca" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1675_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1676_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1678_">Unfortunately, no. The Emma Upholstered Bed Frame has its own suspension that is uniquely designed with FlexiSlats® that help provide additional pressure-relief for your back and joints and an AirFlow® bed base that helps maximize breathability.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1679_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1680_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="0ac6ea44-6c45-45c9-8a2d-8ee55065b2bd" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Do I need to use the Emma Original mattress with it, or would another mattress be fine as well? </span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="0ac6ea44-6c45-45c9-8a2d-8ee55065b2bd" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1682_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1683_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1685_">You can use the bed with any mattress and any topper. To get the best sleep experience, we would of course recommend using an Emma mattress with your Upholstered Bed Frame. If you want to get the Boxspring bed experience, you can add a topper to it too. </span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1686_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1687_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="c9ca2d8e-e550-45b2-bd65-5f94cc6f292c" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>How high is the Upholstered Bed frame?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="c9ca2d8e-e550-45b2-bd65-5f94cc6f292c" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1689_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1690_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1692_">Our Upholstered bedframe has a maximum height of 43 inches (with the headboard) and a bed height of 14 inches without the mattress and 24 inches with the mattress.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1693_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1694_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="b2bd655f-94cc-4f29-acec-f794de717fe5" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>What are the dimensions of your Bed Frames?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="b2bd655f-94cc-4f29-acec-f794de717fe5" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1696_"><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1697_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1698_"><div class="sc-hjGZqJ fbWulc pf-1699_ pf-table-default" data-pf-type="Table"><table><tbody><tr><th class="A1"><span>Size</span></th><th class="B1"><span>Length</span></th><th class="C1"><span>Width</span></th><th class="D1"><span>Height</span></th><th class="E1"><span>Weight</span></th></tr><tr><td class="A2"><span>Full</span></td><td class="B2"><span>75.20 in</span></td><td class="C2"><span>53.94 in</span></td><td class="D2"><span>43.30 in</span></td><td class="E2"><span>121 lbs</span></td></tr><tr><td class="A3"><span>Queen</span></td><td class="B3"><span>79.92 in</span></td><td class="C3"><span>60.24 in</span></td><td class="D3"><span>43.30 in</span></td><td class="E3"><span>129.8 lbs </span></td></tr><tr><td class="A4"><span>King</span></td><td class="B4"><span>79.92 in</span></td><td class="C4"><span>75.98 in</span></td><td class="D4"><span>43.30 in</span></td><td class="E4"><span>158.4 lbs</span></td></tr><tr><td class="A5"><span>California King</span></td><td class="B5"><span>83.86 in</span></td><td class="C5"><span>72.05 in</span></td><td class="D5"><span>43.30 in</span></td><td class="E5"><span>147.4 lbs</span></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1700_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1701_"><h6 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-1702_ header"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1704_">How do I take care of and assemble my bed frame?</span></h6><div class="sc-iCfMLu dkvyUF pf-1705_ pf-icon-left" data-scrolling="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion"><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1706_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1707_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="717fe5c0-39ff-4a04-b472-1676a7442d3b" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>How do I assemble my Upholstered Bed Frame?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="717fe5c0-39ff-4a04-b472-1676a7442d3b" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1709_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1710_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1712_">Assembling the Upholstered Bed Frame may take 30-45 minutes. We have a manual and a video to guide you on this. Please view the manual for instructions <a href="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0562/9873/3706/files/Upholstered_Bedframe_-_Instructions.pdf?v=1658750087" target="_blank">here.</a> For an instructional video, please view <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6GBNFJFQe4Y&amp;ab_channel=EmmaMattress" target="_blank">here.
