</a></span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1974_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1975_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="20e360ee-5891-4469-be09-14a66bdbfdd1" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>How does the Emma Breathable Mattress Protector work?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="20e360ee-5891-4469-be09-14a66bdbfdd1" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1977_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1978_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1980_">The Breathable Mattress Protector has Tri-Protect™ Action. Its polyurethane layer prevents unwanted liquid from getting into the mattress. It also uses Purotex® technology which reduces allergens (i.e. dust mites, animal hair) by up to 93.7%, and is made with a  breathable material. All these keep your mattress well-protected from stains, allergens, and prolongs the useful comfortable life of your mattress.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1981_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1982_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="693e0914-a66b-4bfd-913c-dde6e56306b5" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>What advantages do the probiotic features have?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="693e0914-a66b-4bfd-913c-dde6e56306b5" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1984_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1985_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1987_">The Emma Breathable Mattress Protector’s hypoallergenic nature contains probiotics using Purotex® Technology that allows for a natural repellant from allergies for your comfort in sleep. In simple terms, it reduces the likelihood for allergens to affect you during sleep.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1988_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1989_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="fdd13cdd-e6e5-4306-b584-ecd5ebb33eff" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>How do I put the Emma Breathable Mattress Protector on the mattress?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="fdd13cdd-e6e5-4306-b584-ecd5ebb33eff" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1991_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1992_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1994_">Putting on the Emma Breathable Mattress Protector is quick and easy. It’s adjustable and flexible. You just need to wrap it around your mattress and you’re good to go. For visual instruction, you may view <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FItaOpA7kNM&amp;ab_channel=EmmaMattress" target="_blank">here.
