67-bbcd25245f5d" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-2161_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-2162_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2164_">We offer toppers for 4 sizes for our Emma Firm-to-Soft Reversible Topper:</span></p><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-2165_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-2166_"><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:1px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-fXEqDS fVXmAe pf-2167_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-2168_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2170_">Twin: 75’’ x 38” x 2” (10 lbs) - Best for children, teens, or anyone under six feet tall.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-2171_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2173_">Full: 75” x 54” x 2” (14 lbs) - Best for individuals or couples looking for something compact yet comfortable</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-2174_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2176_">Queen: 80” x 56” x 2” (17 lbs) - Best for individuals or couples who want extra space.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-2177_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2179_">King: 80” x 76” x 2” (22 lbs) - Best for families who sleep together.</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-2180_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-2181_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="7b5abc16-4762-4a3d-83e4-5894d942040f" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>When do I buy the Emma Firm-to-Soft Reversible Topper?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="7b5abc16-4762-4a3d-83e4-5894d942040f" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-2183_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-2184_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2186_">The Emma Firm-to-Soft Reversible Topper is ideal if you want your mattress softness/firmness to change. Our reversible feature allows you to make your mattress feel firmer or softer depending on your preference.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-2187_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-2188_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="3d83e458-94d9-4204-8f8a-c20babcdd5bb" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>What is the cover made of?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="3d83e458-94d9-4204-8f8a-c20babcdd5bb" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-2190_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-2191_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2193_">The Plush UltraDry® Cover of the Firm-to-Soft Reversible Topper is made of 99% Polyester and 1% Elastane. It is a knitted white fabric that is completely detachable from the topper through a zipper.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-2194_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-2195_"><h6 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-2196_ header"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2198_">Is the Emma Reversible Topper right for you?</span></h6><div class="sc-iCfMLu dkvyUF pf-2199_ pf-icon-left" data-scrolling="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion"><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-2200_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-2201_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="056e4792-ebb9-470c-b3ff-a2773d924782" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>How will the Emma Firm-to-Soft Reversible Topper affect my mattress?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="056e4792-ebb9-470c-b3ff-a2773d924782" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-2203_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-2204_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2206_">Adding our Emma Firm-to-Soft Reversible Topper will change the softness/firmness of your mattress, depending on the side that you use.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-2207_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-2208_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="0cf3ffa2-773d-4247-8262-a4e4ad0fa142" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>What weight should I be to enjoy the Emma Firm-to-Soft Reversible Topper?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="0cf3ffa2-773d-4247-8262-a4e4ad0fa142" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-2210_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-2211_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2213_">We recommend the topper to people between 50 kg and 130 kg. </span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-2214_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-2215_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="478262a4-e4ad-4fa1-82db-c87588256990" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>What are the advantages of the Emma Firm-to-Soft Reversible Topper?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable=