mattress protector and sheets?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="3fec939c-527a-42bb-9c38-98a774188143" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-2259_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-2260_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2262_">&nbsp;You should install your Emma Firm-to-Soft Reversible Topper underneath both the mattress protector and sheets. The sum it up, the order of layers should be:</span></p><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-2263_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-2264_"><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:1px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-fXEqDS fVXmAe pf-2265_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-2266_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2268_">Emma Original Mattress</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-2269_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2271_">Emma Emma Firm-to-Soft Reversible Topper</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-2272_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2274_">Emma Breathable Mattress Protector (if applicable)</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-2275_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2277_">Mattress Sheets</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-2278_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-2279_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="367c259a-9c38-4bdf-8b9f-cee52bbe8870" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Can I wash the Emma Firm-to-Soft Reversible Topper?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="367c259a-9c38-4bdf-8b9f-cee52bbe8870" sty